  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Escape a dangerous factory using the power of magnetism. You must team up with three different magnet friends and use their unique abilities to solve more than 50 tricky single-screen puzzles. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685900/extras/0c618f68bf33275feb792859913f6a7e.poster.avif?t=1753080661\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685900/extras/0c618f68bf33275feb792859913f6a7e.webm?t=1753080661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685900/extras/0c618f68bf33275feb792859913f6a7e.mp4?t=1753080661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game comes from Mark Brown, the creator of the YouTube channel Game Maker’s Toolkit. You can follow his game making journey on YouTube... and now play the final result for yourself! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685900/extras/c64ac4636c342c8a426491252c47129d.poster.avif?t=1753080661\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685900/extras/c64ac4636c342c8a426491252c47129d.webm?t=1753080661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2685900/extras/c64ac4636c342c8a426491252c47129d.mp4?t=1753080661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Solve more than 50 puzzles, in 5 different worlds as you work your way up the factory. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Use magnetism to move blocks, open doors, travel over gaps, and more.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Meet a cast of cute magnet friends and borrow their handy problem-solving abilities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Play through the game with developer's commentary to learn how it was made.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
